	* bullet 1. Example if math notation in-line :math:`\phi_{thermal}`
	* bullet 2. Math relation presented separately

		.. math::

		   \bar{\phi} = \phi_{thermal}w_{thermal} + (1-w_{thermal})\phi_{fast}


